title: HOUR 1 - Dallas Cowboys, Lamar Jackson, Brian Billick
itunes:title: HOUR 1 - Dallas Cowboys, Lamar Jackson, Brian Billick
description:
In hour 1, Colin discusses what he thinks will keep Dallas successful when Dak returns to the starting line-up and that's the RUNNING GAME! He also feels as if Lamar Jackson is the only QB not allowed to win games in ugly fashion. Brian Billick joins to talk Matt Rhule, Lamar Jackson and more.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
